- Model performs well for identifying non-buyers. Performance for buyers (`True`) can be improved with more balanced data or pruning.

---

## üå± Tree Visualization

The decision tree was exported and rendered using `Graphviz`. To avoid clutter:
- `max_depth` was limited
- `min_samples_split` was adjusted to simplify branches

